text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This transmits obsolete IRM 2.152.2, Data Engineering, Data Management Process Description.

Obsoletes IRM Part 2 Chapter 152 Data Engineering, Section 2 Data Management dated November 22, 2019 due to Solution Engineering IRM Restructure Project to reﬂect engineering process with projects, and incorporate into the IRM Engineering Chapter a new Section IRM 2.120.11.

All projects following the Enterprise Life Cycle (ELC) and customers who request data management services through the Conﬁguration Management, Change Management KISAM , the Work Request Management System (WRMS), or the OnLine 5081 Service.
